.SH NAME
bcm63xx_udc_set_halt \- Enable/disable STALL flag in the hardware.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" bcm63xx_udc_set_halt
.BI "(struct usb_ep *ep "  ","
.BI "int value "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ep" 12
Endpoint to halt.
.IP "value" 12
Zero to clear halt; nonzero to set halt.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
See comments in \fBbcm63xx_update_wedge\fP.
